pic competitor\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To mark the moment, theyposted on Instagram: I do not know how to feel.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5436736128129403e-36, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel proud seeing \\\"Quinn\\\" up on the lineup and on my accreditation.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Quinn\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"the lineup\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"my accreditation\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel sad knowing there were Olympians before me unable to live their truth because of the world.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"their truth\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel optimistic for change.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Change in legislature.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"legislature\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Changes in rules, structures, and mindsets.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Changes\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"structures\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"mindsets\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mostly, I feel aware of the realities.\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the realities\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trans girls being banned from sports.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trans girls\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trans women facing discrimination and bias while trying to pursue their olympic dreams.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trans women\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"bias\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"their olympic dreams\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fight is not close to over\\u2026 and I will celebrate when we are all here.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fight\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quinn is not the only nonbinary athlete competing in Paris.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quinn_Fabray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.766816102636907e-22, \"text\": \"Quinn\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quinn_Fabray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quinn_Fabray\"}, {\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.2851106807002734e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso