: 5014, \"end\": 5025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5452473630406425e-14, \"text\": \"trans women\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Satoko Itani\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 4933}, {\"ngram\": \"a gender-studies specialist\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4962}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5001}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5034}, {\"ngram\": \"male privilege\", \"from\": 5059, \"to\": 5073}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 5091, \"to\": 5105}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 5115, \"to\": 5123}, {\"ngram\": \"so many other forms\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5158}, {\"ngram\": \"male privilege\", \"from\": 5162, \"to\": 5176}, {\"ngram\": \"women's participation\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5224}, {\"ngram\": \"unequal opportunities\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5252}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5262}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 5267, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 5276, \"to\": 5285}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual harassment\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They noted, \\\"Unlike the fledgling and inconclusive science that anti-trans forces are marshaling to exclude trans women athletes, an abundant body of research exists on these other issues.\\\"\", \"from\": 5326, \"to\": 5515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fledgling\", \"from\": 5346, \"to\": 5359}, {\"ngram\": \"inconclusive science\", \"from\": 5364, \"to\": 5384}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-trans forces\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5407}, {\"ngram\": \"trans women athletes\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5454}, {\"ngram\": \"an abundant body\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5472}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5484}, {\"ngram\": \"these other issues\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Travers, a professor of sociology at Simon Fraser University, said that these rules do more than marginalize trans girls and women at all levels of sports, from elementary school to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5517, \"to\": 5712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5554, \"end\": 5577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Fraser_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5247463874230354e-18, \"text\": \"Simon Fraser University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Fraser_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Fraser_University\"}, {\"begin\": 5626, \"end\": 5631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3580643139811202e-18, \"text\": \"trans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Travers\", \"from\": 5517, \"to\": 5524}, {\"ngram\": \"a professor\", \"from\": 5526, \"to\": 5537}, {\"ngram\": \"sociology\", \"from\": 5541, \"to\": 5550}, {\"ngram\": \"these rules\", \"from\": 5589, \"to\": 5600}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5642, \"to\": 5647}, {\"ngram\": \"all levels\", \"from\": 5651, \"to\": 5661}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5671}, {\"ngram\": \"elementary school\", \"from\": 5678, \"to\": 5695}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also feed a far greater right-wing current in the United States and around the world.\", \"from\": 5713, \"to\": 5803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5768, \"end\": 5781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998339477845377, \"rank\": 0.00016607979369548482, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_